actions.message:
Hi ${tempVars("Owner")}!
---------------------------- 

Thanks for adding me to `${tempVars("ServerName")}` :fire: 

For help on the bot Join the support server here: https://discord.gg/evXZAE5  

Also please send feedback by typing: `cb!request (Your feedback here)`

:boom:  𝘼𝘿𝙈𝙄𝙉 𝘾𝙊𝙈𝙈𝘼𝙉𝘿𝙎 (𝙈𝙐𝙎𝙏 𝙃𝘼𝙑𝙀 𝘼𝘿𝙈𝙄𝙉 𝙍𝙊𝙇𝙀𝙎)  :boom: 

:cheese:  `cb!info`   Shows the set server info.

:cheese:  `cb!cchat`   I will clear the specified number of chat messages from the channel.

:cheese:  `cb!defaultrole`   When set, I will assign this role to new members.

:cheese:  `cb!welcomechannel` When set, I will welcome new members to this server in that channel.

:cheese:  `cb!welcomemessage` When set, I will send new members the message you set to them in a DM.

:ballot_box_with_check:  𝙂𝙀𝙉𝙀𝙍𝘼𝙇 𝘾𝙊𝙈𝙈𝘼𝙉𝘿𝙎 (𝙀𝙑𝙀𝙍𝙔𝙊𝙉𝙀 𝘾𝘼𝙉 𝙐𝙎𝙀)  :ballot_box_with_check: 

:cheese:  `cb!help`   Shows commands and help for the bot.

:cheese:  `cb!request`   I will send a request to the bot owner to add a feature! Example: `cb!request Add more stuff`

:cheese:  `cb!ascii`   Transforms the text to an Ascii image.  Example: `cb!ascii Hello`

:musical_note:  𝙈𝙐𝙎𝙄𝘾 𝘾𝙊𝙈𝙈𝘼𝙉𝘿𝙎  :musical_note: 

:cheese:  `cb!play`   I will join your voice channel and start playing the song that you requested after the command! Example: `cb!play [SONG NAME]`

:cheese:  `cb!clearqueue`   Clears the song queue

:cheese:  `cb!disconnect`   Disconnects the bot from the voice channel

:cheese: `cb!skip`   Skips the current song
